text: Samraong Commune () is a khum (commune) in Samraŏng District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, Samraong Commune has 9 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable mw-collapsible" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21070801 |Kansaom Ak |កន្សោមអក |- !2 |21070802 |Dei Kraham |ដីក្រហម |- !3 |21070803 |Prey Totueng |ព្រៃទទឹង |- !4 |21070804 |Samraong |សំរោង |- !5 |21070805 |Tuol Char |ទួលចារ |- !6 |21070806 |Ta Poun Khang Kaeut |តាពោនខាងកើត |- !7 |21070807 |Ta Poun Khang Lech |តាពោនខាងលិច |- !8 |21070808 |Krang Ro'out |ក្រាំងរអូត |- !9 |21070809 |Svay |ស្វាយ |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Samraong District
